nodes.text: Tikiars were starfighters manufactured in the Senex sector, but it was not uncommon to see them in some sections of the Outer Rim. A number of these fighters, together with Z-95 Headhunters, attacked Sentinel Base fourteen years before the Battle of Yavin. The Tikiars and Headhunters present in this engagement were modified with basic hyperdrives and upgraded weaponry.
